name: Let There Be Life
description:
A celebration of our beginnings:
the birth of the universe, our sun,
the Earth, and life itself, in an
endless cycle that begins with the
singularity, and ends with the
watershed moment of
multicellularity, an evolutionary
invention that may ultimately lead
to new universes -- beginning the
cycle anew. 2560x1440, 30s loop.
A carbon-negative NFT: every bid
will be matched by a carbon offset
of at least 1,000 pounds of C02.
